xua-album" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处预订</a>）。</p><p>到目前为止，她已经分享了这张唱片的三种口味。九月，她放弃了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-announces-new-album-eusexua-and-shares-pulsating-title-track-3793581">专辑的主打歌</a>，并附有乔丹·海明威执导的音乐录影带，紧随其后的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-shares-intoxicating-single-perfect-stranger-with-phoebe-waller-bridge-and-yves-tumor-cameos-3804104">《完美陌生人》，</a>其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-waller-bridge">菲比·沃勒-布里奇</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yves-tumor">伊夫·图莫尔</a>客串了这首歌。</p><p>最近，她发行了与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/koreless">Koreless</a>合作的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-fka-twigs-avant-garde-new-single-with-koreless-drums-of-death-3813008">前卫单曲“Drums Of Death”</a> 。</p><p> 《Eusexua》在<a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-songs-2024"><em>NME</em> 2024 年 50 首最佳歌曲排行榜</a>中名列第 21 位，这首歌被誉为“对 techno 的惊人而精致的诠释”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3769216" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3769216" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3769216" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024.jpg" alt="FKA Twigs（摄影：Marleen Moise/Getty Images）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/FKA-Twigs-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3769216" class="wp-caption-text"> FKA Twigs（摄影：Marleen Moise/Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>在其他地方，Cocker 最近几个月一直在煽动有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pulp">Pulp</a>新材料的谣言，此前他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-first-gig-of-2025-confirmed-with-manic-street-preachers-weezer-primal-scream-3784018">最近被一位歌迷在 Walthamstow 发现，并据报道告诉他们乐队将“回到录音室”</a> 。</p><p>就在几天前，Pulp 在 Flow Festival 2024 上表演，并使用他们的布景首次推出了一<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulp-debut-a-sunset-at-flow-festival-watch-footage-setlist-3782859">首名为“A Sunset”的新歌，该歌曲由 Richard Hawley 共同创作</a>。</p><p>在此之前，这位主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jarvis-cocker-teases-more-pulp-shows-and-discusses-new-project-biophobia-i-used-to-be-scared-of-nature-3595600">接受<em>NME</em>采访</a>，表示这首歌可能会在某个时候正式发行，并确认 Pulp 2025 年的巡演计划。乐队将于 1 月份在日本<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pulps-first-gig-of-2025-confirmed-with-manic-street-preachers-weezer-primal-scream-3784018">Rockin&#39; On Sonic 音乐节上</a>进行今年的首次约会。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/manic-street-preachers">《狂躁街传教士》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">《原始尖叫》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-lemon-twigs">《柠檬枝》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wednesday">《星期三》</a>等。</p><p> Pulp 的最后一张完整专辑是 2001 年的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-5728-339234">We Love Life”</a> 。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-5728-339234">对该唱片的三星级评论</a>中， <em>NME</em>将这张唱片描述为“由简洁的管弦乐和白光合唱间奏所支撑的宏伟的交响乐事件”。它补充道：“有时，当音乐在科克阴郁的口语冥想之上翱翔时，它真的闪闪发光。”</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fka-twigs-jarvis-cocker-munroe-bergdorf-marcel-dettman-annie-mac-lead-ava-london-line-up-buy-tickets-3819400">FKA Twigs、Jarvis Cocker、Munroe Bergdorf、Marcel Dettman、Annie Mac 领军的 AVA London 阵容</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
