"noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>报道，卡迪夫市议会表示，在许可批准之前开始售票是“常见做法”，并且该活动将“巩固卡迪夫作为主要艺术家的音乐中心的地位”。</p><p>他们补充说，正在采取特别措施，防止公园的板球场遭到破坏。</p><p>一般销售将于明天（12 月 6 日） <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fblackweir-tickets-cardiff%2Fvenue%2F254751" target="_blank" rel="noopener">上午</a>9 点开始。 </p><figure id="attachment_3790384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3790384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3790384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City.jpg" alt="Caleb Followill 与 Kings Of Leon 一起在舞台上现场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/KingsOfLeon-Joes-Head-Song-For-The-City-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3790384" class="wp-caption-text"> Caleb Followill 与 Kings Of Leon 一起现场表演。图片来源：里克·科恩/盖蒂</figcaption></figure><p>除了卡迪夫演出之外，乐队还确认将于 7 月 2 日在兰开夏郡莱瑟姆音乐节上于 2025 年夏季举行另一场演出。</p><p>这是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/justin-timberlake">贾斯汀·汀布莱克 (Justin Timberlake)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alanis-morissette">艾拉妮丝·莫莉塞特 (Alanis Morissette)</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simple-minds">Simple Minds</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/texas">Texas</a>将在 2025 年音乐节上表演之后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/justin-ti